ds, responsibilities, and rewards of family, friends, motherhood, and grandmotherhood are ultimately accepted, together with those of a working artist.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2022) 0aArtistszUnited StatesvBiography. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / Diaries & Journals.2bisacsh1 aKushner, Rachel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTruitt, Alexandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022 Englishz978311099375208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022z9783110993738oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311074977940uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300264326?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300264326423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300264326/original  a978-3-11-074977-9  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099375-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DKUb2022